I understand that my actions were not in line with the principles of good character that I have upheld in the past. Prior to this incident, I have strived to maintain an exemplary record, free from any criminal activities. Unfortunately, in this particular instance, I allowed myself to be influenced by external factors and made a regrettable decision. I deeply regret my involvement in accepting the bribe and recognize the gravity of the consequences.

It is important to note that this incident was an aberration from my usual conduct. I have always placed a great emphasis on ethical behavior and integrity, which is evidenced by my clean record. I want to emphasize that this incident should not overshadow the honesty and responsibility that I have consistently demonstrated throughout my life.

Furthermore, I acknowledge that my acceptance of the bribe did not have a significant impact on the overall outcome. The information regarding the company's deceptive practices was later exposed by someone else just five weeks after I accepted the bribe. This demonstrates that even without my involvement, the truth would have come to light in a timely manner.

In conclusion, Your Honour, I stand before you today to accept full responsibility for the actions I have taken. I am deeply remorseful for allowing myself to be swayed by external influences and straying from the path of good character. I assure you that this experience has been a wake-up call and I am committed to learning from it and bettering myself as a result. I will continue to uphold the values of honesty, integrity, and responsibility that I have adhered to in the past.

Thank you for your attention to this matter.

Respectfully,

